Package: llmshieldr
Title: Security Scanning and Policy Enforcement for LLM Workflows
Version: 0.1.1
Description: Provides preflight scanning, redaction, policy-based action
    selection, postflight output checks, and audit logging for large language
    model (LLM) workflows in R. Includes rule-based detection of secrets,
    personally identifiable or protected health information, prompt injection
    patterns, and domain-specific output risks. Can also use a local reviewer
    model through Ollama-compatible chat clients for privacy-first semantic
    checks. Designed for regulated workflows and extensible to
    project-specific policies.
